          "date": "2011-10-01 20:40:40.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-641 obdclass: use rwlock for obd_dev_lock",
        "message": "LU-641 obdclass: use rwlock for obd_dev_lock\n\nIn target_handle_connect() it grabs obd_dev_lock to find obd_device\nby target uuid. This causes lock contention if there are two many connection\nrequests on the same time. Based on obd_dev_lock is a read-mostly lock, it\nis much reasonable to revise it as a rwlock.\n\nChange-Id: I7f936d6182df9e7ed46b8a1b6fb259226188acbc\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jay@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
